---
// Astro component frontmatter
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}favicon.png`} />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Thank You - KiwiTicket</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Thank you for 5 amazing years with KiwiTicket. We're grateful to all our producers and customers who made this journey possible." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Thank You - KiwiTicket" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Thank you for 5 amazing years with KiwiTicket. We're grateful to all our producers and customers who made this journey possible." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:image" content={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/kiwiticket_logo.svg`} />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://kiwiticket.github.io/farewell" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Thank You - KiwiTicket" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Thank you for 5 amazing years with KiwiTicket. We're grateful to all our producers and customers who made this journey possible." />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/kiwiticket_logo.svg`} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta name="author" content="KiwiTicket" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="KiwiTicket, ticketing, New Zealand, farewell, thank you, event ticketing" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://kiwiticket.github.io/farewell" />

  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <div class="logo-header">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/kiwiticket_logo.svg`} alt="KiwiTicket Logo" class="logo" />
        <h1 class="brand-name">KiwiTicket</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2 class="title">Thank You</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">
          After 5 incredible years, KiwiTicket is saying goodbye
        </p>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="message">
            <p>
              To all our amazing <span class="highlight">event producers</span> who trusted us with their dreams and to every
              <span class="highlight">ticket buyer</span> who discovered something special through our platform,
              <strong>thank you</strong>.
            </p>

            <p>
              For five years, we've been privileged to be part of New Zealand's vibrant events scene.
              From intimate gigs to outdoor concerts, comedy festivals to high school productions, community fundraisers to cultural celebrations,
              you made KiwiTicket more than just a ticketing platform, you made it a community.
            </p>

            <p>
              While this chapter is closing, the memories, connections, and experiences you've all created
              will live on. Thank you for letting us be part of your journey.
            </p>

            <p>
              <em>Ngā mihi and farewell,<br />The KiwiTicket Team</em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <p class="contact">
          For any questions or support, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:help@kiwiticket.co.nz" class="contact-email">help@kiwiticket.co.nz</a>
        </p>
        <p class="farewell">
          2019 - 2025 • KiwiTicket
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
